{"tid":1584560,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［建議］發夢夢見去黨鐵車廠參觀","createTime":"2019-09-21T07:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T10:33:32.000Z","uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f306f96a13797bdfc2fe955df6bd1318bcdbb9ce","tid":1584560,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">黨鐵視香港人如狗，於是我哋用唔同行動抵制黨鐵，包括逃票、玩轉車站。其實仲有一個戰線我哋未玩過，就係車廠！<br />\n<br />\n車廠地址：<br />\n高鐵 石崗車廠<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">港島綫 柴灣車廠</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">觀塘綫 九龍灣車廠</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣綫 荃灣車廠</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">將軍澳綫 康城車廠</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">南港島綫 黃竹坑車廠</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">東涌綫及機鐵 小蠔灣車廠</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">東鐵綫 火炭車廠</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">西鐵綫 錦田車廠</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">馬鞍山綫 大圍車廠</span><br />\n輕鐵 屯門車廠<br />\n<br />\n其實而家跳閘已經冇以前咁有效，因為罰款調高咗去到5000，甚至俾狗拉，又有secure睇9住閘機，有時仲有埋狗、藍屍喺站度。與其跳閘先懲罰到黨鐵十幾廿蚊，我哋要尋求其他方法用更大金額懲罰黨鐵，所以玩轉車站要做，玩轉車廠更加要做！<br />\n<br />\n車廠好處：<br />\n1. 地方大<br />\n2. 搞轉啲車、維修設施，少啲正常嘅車用，咁大家又唔使返工返學<br />\n<br />\n如果有咩建議 歡迎指正<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f8ad62f1a87f049e808c89490865dbc75797c7","tid":1584560,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:41:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"6e7fb335f576cb63ef3fb1d2d970cf54ee62cfe0","tid":1584560,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052c1f0ae0456009edaf87cb88cfdf3bfa888fa5","tid":1584560,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:41:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"691928d9be10c441a76075ac7112364ac07bf480","tid":1584560,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c6b36127256b39fd6f271bcbc6231c1552ad521","tid":1584560,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:44:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"173cc43bae75fd8d2cdf76a7e9c8c1db90170598","tid":1584560,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:47:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動係咪壽終正寢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563531</a><br />\n<br />\n［熱門唔該］冇人講監控燈柱查到啲咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560935</a><br />\n<br />\n[學術研究]水馬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1336880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1336880</a><br />\n<br />\n和理非奇招: 寄信輸出革命2<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528683</a><br />\n<br />\n［建議］發夢夢見去黨鐵車廠參觀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584560</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇人想喺狗隻招募日做現場宣傳？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380083</a>"},{"pid":"5d59